snippet.title: CYGNI: All Guns Blazing Story Trailer
snippet.description:
The new atmospheric Story trailer showcases a cinematic inspiring call to arms, alongside mind-bending high-octane action in never-before-seen levels – all in stunning next-generation visuals!

Wishlist the game now on Steam® and Playstation®5:

· STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1248080/CYGNI_All_Guns_Blazing/ · PS5: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10004231/

Keep an eye on the dedicated channels for further information and updates:

· Twitter - CygniGame

· Facebook - CygniGame

· Discord - Cygni

· TikTok - CygniGame
